---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const _b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout title="Iboga – Key Information" description="Everything you need to know about iboga: effects, dosage, safety, legal status in Germany and how to get started." image="/images/iboga-plant.jpg" locale="en">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-earth-900">Key Information</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-earth-600">Everything you need to know about iboga – concise and clear.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8 text-earth-700 leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-3">What is Iboga?</h2>
          <p>Iboga is a plant from Central Africa containing the psychoactive compound ibogaine. Ibogaine can cause significant physical and psychological changes. It supports personal and spiritual development, mindfulness, cleansing, and shadow work.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-3">How does Iboga work?</h2>
          <p>Small amounts (up to 5 mg/kg) have a stimulating effect; higher doses are psychedelic and hallucinogenic. Iboga root causes deep insights into the true underlying causes of a person's core problems. Onset is between 30 and 180 minutes after ingestion, often announced by a ringing in the ears. Duration is 18 to 36 hours.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-3">What is iboga used for?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Addiction (heroin, alcohol, nicotine, medication)</li>
            <li>PTSD and trauma</li>
            <li>Mood and personality disorders</li>
            <li>Spiritual development and personal growth</li>
            <li>Depression and anxiety</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-3">Is iboga safe?</h2>
          <p>Iboga is very safe when used correctly. The precise adherence to preparation protocols is crucial. For flood doses, professional guidance is always required.</p>
          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm font-medium">⚠️ Microdosing can safely be done alone. Professional guidance is mandatory for flood doses.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-3">Legal status in Germany</h2>
          <p>Iboga treatment exists in a legal grey zone in Germany. It is not an illegal narcotic. Possession and consumption are permitted, allowing private individuals to offer ibogaine treatments.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-3">Why is iboga expensive?</h2>
          <p>The iboga plant is endangered due to overharvesting. Prices have nearly increased tenfold in recent years. Some suppliers like Iboga Store use sustainable cultivation methods.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
      <aside class="space-y-6">
        <img src={`${_b}/images/iboga-plant.jpg`} alt="Tabernanthe Iboga" class="w-full rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-md aspect-square" />
        <div class="bg-forest-50 border border-forest-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-forest-800 mb-2">Buy Iboga</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-forest-700 mb-3">Sustainably grown products from our own plantation in Ghana.</p>
          <a href="https://iboga.store/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-center px-4 py-2 bg-forest-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-forest-700 transition-colors">
            Iboga Store ↗
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
